halos-homarr-branding (0.1.0-3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Use complete Homarr v1.x schema template instead of custom tables
  * Include Drizzle migration records so Homarr skips migrations
  * Replace halos-service user with admin user for API key ownership
  * Set admin user provider='oidc' for OIDC account matching
  * Add email 'admin@halos.local' for OIDC account linking
  * Add admin user to admins group with admin permissions

